# {{lb|en|arts}} The scheme of two or more [[color]]s in which a design is available. It is often used to describe variegated or ombre (shades of one color) print [[yarn]]s, [[fabric]], or [[thread]]. It can also be applied to [[apparel]], to [[wallpaper]] and other [[interior design]] [[motifs]], and to specifications for [[printed]] [[material]]s such as [[magazines]] or [[newspapers]].

